{"tid":675042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"煙盒警告標語都幾惡毒吓喎!","createTime":"2018-05-23T08:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T08:45:22.000Z","uid":119688,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e47881d629ac8d36ab70ec51ed82054bca7558","tid":675042,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"唔係煙民平時無留意<br />\n但知道咩叫臭腳 <br />\n就係煙盒上爛腳既警告<br />\n<br />\n今日同個煙鏟朋友食lunch<br />\n見佢銀包同包煙都放上檯<br />\n<br />\n無聊留意左陣見到應該唔係新<br />\n係我頭一次見既警告標語<br />\n黑白畫面一個男人含住枝煙拎住佢老婆張車頭相<br />\n<br />\n以唔食煙既角度黎睇都幾諷刺<br />\n心諗煙民要食你政府點樣創意個警告標語都無用<br />\n<br />\n最後都係果句 你地都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟肺癌仆街死</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5d6495220521be5a21f2f45dc714886dc32e9110","tid":675042,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92631a057d599045bd6d887e6fd469d04f04c7ca","tid":675042,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"女權撚唔抗議？ 點解死嘅係女人"},{"pid":"8297444ea77dfb2a25aacc87d033b3558a0f9b97","tid":675042,"uid":58201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"火車頭正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60cae28dd4c728c45c0d8bb8f0dc0619c722b8a","tid":675042,